  "lookup_id": "94.8",
  "title": "94.8",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "h5",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "READ ONE:"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "link": {
            "id": null,
            "anchor": "read-one",
            "url": "#read-one"
          }
        }
      ],
      "anchor": "read-one"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you\u2019ve completed"
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "RESCUE (VIRA):"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You\u2019re sitting in your tent, just waking up, when there\u2019s a shout\nfrom the path. Zek Tsal is riding by on his stilt-horse. He doesn\u2019t\nstop, but tosses you a bundle and calls \u201cVira says thanks for\nsaving her!\u201d before riding away. You unwrap it to find stacks of\nfragrantly spiced pemmican."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Each Ranger gains one energy in an aspect of their choice for the\nfirst round."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you\u2019re currently on"
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "RESCUE (VIRA):"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Vira has stopped responding, and her breathing is shallow. You can\u2019t move her, but you\u2019re worried she may suffer permanent injury without the help of a healer. All you can do is light a smoky signal fire and hope for rescue."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Luckily, that evening you see the Swift soaring through the sky to your position. You later learn that a boat along the Silverfin spotted the smoke and reported it once they reached their destination. You load Vira onto the Swift. A few moments later the glider launches high into the air, on its way to Lone Tree."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Complete"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "RESCUE (VIRA)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and record"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "HELPED RESCUE VIRA"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "on the campaign tracker."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Otherwise:"
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You receive word from a stilt-horse courier that Vira has been found. Apparently when nobody else went looking for her, Kal Iver went out and found her nearly unconscious at the base of a tree. Thankfully, her injuries were treatable, and everyone expects a full recovery."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "If you have"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "SEARCH (VIRA)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", complete it. If you don't, gain that mission and immediately complete it. Record"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "KAL RESCUED VIRA"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "on the campaign tracker."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "items": [],
